content:
[[iftags +コンポーネント・バックエンド]]
[[note]]
このユーザーコンポーネントのリファレンスは[[[reference:new-message|]]]です。
[[/note]]
[[/iftags]]

[[module CSS]]
.new-message > .colmod-block > ul > li.folded > ul:not([style]) + .colmod-link-top a:nth-child(1),
.new-message > .colmod-block > ul > li.unfolded > .colmod-link-top a:nth-child(2) {
    display: none;
}
.new-message > .colmod-block > ul > li.folded > ul[style*="none"] + .colmod-link-top a:nth-child(1) {
    display: inline;
}
.new-message > .colmod-block > ul > li.folded > ul:not([style]) + .colmod-link-top a:nth-child(2) {
    display: inline;
    font-weight: bold;
    animation: blink 0.6s infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes blink {
    0% { opacity:0; }
    80%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
}
.new-message > .colmod-block > ul > li > .colmod-link-top.align-center {
    text-align: center;
}
[[/module]]

[[div class="new-message"]]
[[div_ class="colmod-block"]]
[[ul]][[li class="folded"]][[ul]]_[[/ul]][[div class="colmod-link-top align-{$align}"]]
[[div_ class="foldable-list-container"]]
[# {$open}][# {$first-open}][# {$close}][[/div]][[/div]][[div class="colmod-content"]]
